{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act27side_level_act27side_st03","storyGroup":"act27side","storySort":19,"storyDependence":"act27side_level_act27side_08_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"SL-ST-3","storyName":"晴天","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"凯勒终于说出瑙曼夫妇去世的真相和自己的心结，艾雅法拉发现凯勒的名字也叫阿黛尔。埃尼斯在医院醒来，听说决定不再搬迁风情街，而是修建水上乐园。在小店其乐融融的氛围中，艾雅法拉终于拿起笔，写完给父母的回信。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act27side/level_act27side_st03","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act27side_st03","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":17,"characters":["寻找汐斯塔的少女","大帝","伯德","阿黛尔","凯勒","埃尼斯","锡兰","黑","哈莉","亚当斯","魏彦吾","温和的生物","严肃的生物"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/57/Avg_bg_41_g11_volcanomountainside.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/a001/m_dia_path_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":8},{"type":"text","text":"有生态学者，将这片大地上所有的羽兽分为了两类，“候羽”与“留羽”。","id":9},{"type":"text","text":"前者会因为气候、生态的变化，不断搬迁，寻找最适合自己生存的地方；而后者一旦安家，就会永远留下，想方设法地守护好家园。","id":10},{"type":"text","text":"这一生物学说后来被历史学家借用，有人提出，“大地上所有族群之间的矛盾，都是只能生活在一个地方的人和四处漂流的人的矛盾”。","id":11},{"type":"text","text":"在这之后，又有人对这种观点提出了补充。","id":12},{"type":"text","text":"这片大地上原本没有留羽，但是慢慢地，羽兽们在某个地方聚集，一起建构家园，创造共同的回忆，也就出现了留羽。","id":13},{"type":"text","text":"......","id":14},{"type":"dialog","id":15},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":16},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":17},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.3","fadetime":"1","id":18},{"type":"charslot","id":19},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":20},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":21},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":22},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":23},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":24},{"type":"dialogue","name":"寻找汐斯塔的少女","text":"这次一定不会搞错了，按地图上的路线，翻过这座山头就是汐斯塔了。","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"寻找汐斯塔的少女","text":"汐斯塔，是在这里吧......","id":26},{"type":"text","text":"放眼望去，目之所及，只剩一片雪白。","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"寻找汐斯塔的少女","text":"这......这是哪啊？！","id":28},{"type":"dialog","id":29},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":30},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":31},{"type":"charslot","id":32},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5e/Avg_bg_41_g7_siestahightechtouristzone.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":33},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":34},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"1","id":35},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":36},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":37},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"char_105_emper","duration":"0.7","id":38},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_993_1#4$1","duration":"0.7","id":39},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":40},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"char_105_emper","focus":"l","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大帝","text":"哟，好久不见了。","id":42,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/75/Avg_char_105_emper.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_993_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯德","text":"咦，不是为了参加黑曜石音乐节，大帝先生又为什么会光临这里？您的衣服，好像烧破了一个洞......？","id":44,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_993_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"char_105_emper","focus":"l","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大帝","text":"我们应该立即马上换一个话题。","id":46,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/75/Avg_char_105_emper.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_993_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯德","text":"这几天收集到了很不错的素材，回哥伦比亚后应该可以很快创作出一张专辑。","id":48,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_avg_npc_993_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"char_105_emper","focus":"l","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大帝","text":"能让我有所期待的音乐家已经不多了，伯德，你可以算一个。","id":50,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/75/Avg_char_105_emper.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_993_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯德","text":"不禁想起了参加第一届黑曜石音乐节的时候，芭芭拉女士和我说起过她想象中的汐斯塔的将来。","id":52,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/17/Avg_avg_npc_993_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯德","text":"如果有一天，这座城市离开了火山和黑曜石，离开了风景迷人的海岸线，那么这座城市还剩什么呢？","id":53,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/17/Avg_avg_npc_993_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯德","text":"她说音乐是一种载体，但生活在这的人们才是最重要的载体。","id":54,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/17/Avg_avg_npc_993_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_993_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯德","text":"只要还有人会愿意在开心或不开心时唱歌，愿意在傍晚来临时欣赏一会晚霞，汐斯塔就还是那个汐斯塔。","id":56,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_avg_npc_993_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"char_105_emper","focus":"l","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大帝","text":"年轻人不要总是那么怀旧，不然创作出的音乐也会变得老掉牙的。","id":58,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/75/Avg_char_105_emper.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_993_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯德","text":"这就有点强人所难了大帝先生。","id":60,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_avg_npc_993_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯德","text":"即使是在人短暂的一生当中，如果不时时回顾一下自己是怎样一路走来的，也会感到迷失方向的。","id":61,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_avg_npc_993_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯德","text":"还是要偶尔回头看看，是不是有什么珍贵的东西被落在了路上。","id":62,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_avg_npc_993_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"char_105_emper","focus":"l","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大帝","text":"如今过去的一切都埋在那座火山下了，怎么样，要不要准备策划一下黑曜石音乐节2.0？正好我有一些投资打算。","id":64,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/75/Avg_char_105_emper.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_993_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯德","text":"要重新举办的话，是不是该新起一个名字？","id":66,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_avg_npc_993_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_993_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伯德","text":"火山音乐节？好像还是太普通了一点......对了，这次来到汐斯塔，我见到了一种很可爱的动物。就叫“棉花糖音乐节”怎么样？","id":68,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2e/Avg_avg_npc_993_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"char_105_emper","focus":"l","id":69},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大帝","text":"真棒，伯德。你起名字的品味不及你乐品的千分之一。","id":70,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/75/Avg_char_105_emper.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":71},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":72},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":73},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":74},{"type":"charslot","id":75},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4b/Avg_bg_41_g8_siestavolcanomuseum_inside.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":76},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":77},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_warm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":78,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":79},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":80},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2","duration":"0.7","id":81},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_999_1#8$1","duration":"0.7","id":82},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":83},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2","focus":"l","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿黛尔","text":"凯勒老师，火山观测资料都在这里了。","id":85,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3e/Avg_avg_1016_agoat2_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿黛尔","text":"这次观测得到了很有价值的资料，我会把它们整理完之后再回去。","id":86,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3e/Avg_avg_1016_agoat2_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_999_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"辛苦你了......","id":88,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/18/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"你果然已经是一个可以独当一面的学者了，卡提亚和玛格娜会为你感到骄傲的......","id":89,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/18/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"这件防护服也......比起在展柜中，果然还是......","id":90,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/18/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_999_1#8$1","focus":"none","id":91},{"type":"text","text":"学者的声音低了下去，她久久凝视着这件熟悉的外套。","id":92},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2","focus":"l","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿黛尔","text":"我想带着母亲的防护服去踏上更多的火山，它会保护我的。也谢谢您这段时间的指导，我学到了很多......","id":94,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3e/Avg_avg_1016_agoat2_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2","focus":"l","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿黛尔","text":"对了，卡恩前辈呢？","id":96,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3e/Avg_avg_1016_agoat2_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_999_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"因为一些工作，提前返回莱塔尼亚了。","id":98,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/18/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1016_agoat2_1#2$2","focus":"l","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿黛尔","text":"凯勒老师，我想替卡恩前辈向您道歉，他应该是误会了什么......","id":100,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3c/Avg_avg_1016_agoat2_1-2$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_999_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"......我不会在意。","id":102,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/18/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_999_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"阿黛尔......你从来没有怀疑过我？","id":104,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4b/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_999_1#10$1","focus":"none","id":105},{"type":"text","text":"阿黛尔轻轻摇了摇头。","id":106},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1016_agoat2_1#9$2","focus":"l","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿黛尔","text":"我不知道......","id":108,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/11/Avg_avg_1016_agoat2_1-9$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿黛尔","text":"那段时间的事我知道的很少，好像所有人都在有意瞒着我一样。","id":109,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/11/Avg_avg_1016_agoat2_1-9$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿黛尔","text":"但是我看过父母的笔记，还有那些照片......","id":110,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/11/Avg_avg_1016_agoat2_1-9$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿黛尔","text":"我没法相信，一个和他们一同去过那么多火山，共同经历过那么多次危险的人，会做出背叛他们的事......","id":111,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/11/Avg_avg_1016_agoat2_1-9$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_999_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"我有东西，想给你看。","id":113,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8c/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_999_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":114},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"卡恩这几天一直想找的，应该就是这些东西吧。","id":115,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/60/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"这些文件，除了莱塔尼亚官方档案库，只有我手上的一份。","id":116,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/60/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"是废弃的文件，已经算不上什么机密，我只是希望永远不会有人再找到它......","id":117,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/60/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":118},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_999_1#1$1","focus":"none","id":119},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cardboard","volume":"1","id":120},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":121},{"type":"text","text":"学者从书柜中拿出一方纸箱，两位学者存在过的痕迹，容纳在这一方小小的箱子里。","id":122},{"type":"text","text":"陈旧的文件袋上写着“高级机密”之类的字样，上面还盖着“已废弃”的印章。","id":123},{"type":"text","text":"“阵雨计划”。","id":124},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1016_agoat2_1#4$2","focus":"l","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿黛尔","text":"这就是......爸爸的研究军用化的项目吗......","id":126,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/94/Avg_avg_1016_agoat2_1-4$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_999_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"卡提亚和玛格娜毕生的愿望，就是当一名纯粹的学者，他们的确在竭尽全力地去践行这个理想。","id":128,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/60/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"但现实往往是很难纯粹的......","id":129,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/60/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"莱塔尼亚二十多年前政变的余波，贵族之间的纠纷始终在纠缠着他们。为了研究能进行下去，他们不得不做出妥协。","id":130,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/60/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"卡提亚将自己一部分研究成果交给了军队，以换取相对安稳的学术环境。我则是帮他分担了后续的一些对接工作。","id":131,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/60/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"但是他们将希望寄托在了你的身上。","id":132,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/60/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"他们希望可以将这些不纯粹的纠纷阻隔在你的生活之外，让你可以心无旁骛地去研究你感兴趣的问题。","id":133,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/60/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"这也是，我的愿望......","id":134,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/60/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":135},{"type":"charslot","duration":"0.3","id":136},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":137},{"type":"text","text":"我希望多年后，人们提起瑙曼夫妇时，只会记得他们是纯粹而伟大的科研学者，我希望他们唯一的孩子，可以无忧无虑地探索知识。","id":138},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1016_agoat2_1#2$2","focus":"l","id":139},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_999_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿黛尔","text":"爸爸妈妈......他们的牺牲，真的是意外吗......","id":141,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3c/Avg_avg_1016_agoat2_1-2$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_999_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":142},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"那次乌纳火山的考察，在我们准备登山前，来自莱塔尼亚的使者再一次找了上来。","id":143,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/60/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"我希望他们可以不受干扰地完成那次考察，便提出去帮他们搪塞军方。我没有预料到会有那样的意外......","id":144,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/60/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"阿黛尔，我不敢说请求你的原谅......","id":145,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/60/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2","focus":"l","id":146},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿黛尔","text":"凯勒老师，您为什么会觉得，这是自己的错呢？","id":147,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3e/Avg_avg_1016_agoat2_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_999_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"......","id":149,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fe/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2","focus":"l","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿黛尔","text":"我不会因为这些事质疑爸爸妈妈对科研热爱的纯粹，当然也不会质疑凯勒老师您。","id":151,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3e/Avg_avg_1016_agoat2_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿黛尔","text":"你们已经为理想的事业付出全部的努力了，如果还要因此受到指责，那是不是，太不公平了......","id":152,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3e/Avg_avg_1016_agoat2_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2","focus":"l","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿黛尔","text":"爸爸妈妈，应该也是这么想的......","id":154,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3e/Avg_avg_1016_agoat2_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_999_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"我永远会记得那个卡提亚和玛格娜来到汐斯塔的夏天，遇见他们，是我人生中最幸运的事。","id":156,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/18/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":157},{"type":"charslot","duration":"0.3","id":158},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":159},{"type":"text","text":"那一天，有一对陌生的外国游客走进了那家咖啡店，坐在了我的邻桌，我的生活从此被改变了。","id":160},{"type":"text","text":"我见识到了书本之外更广阔美丽的大地，度过了自己的人生中最美好的一段时光。","id":161},{"type":"text","text":"从汐斯塔到莱塔尼亚，还有许多地方，许多座火山，许多次冒险。","id":162},{"type":"text","text":"我多想陪他们再走一段。","id":163},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2","focus":"l","id":164},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_999_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿黛尔","text":"凯勒老师，我可以拥抱您一下吗？","id":166,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3e/Avg_avg_1016_agoat2_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_999_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"......","id":168,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/18/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":169},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_999_1#8$1","focus":"all","id":170},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":171},{"type":"charslot","duration":"0.5","id":172},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":173},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cloakmovement","volume":"0.6","id":174},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":175},{"type":"text","text":"学者将女孩拥入怀中，用额头轻轻抵住她的额头。","id":176},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1016_agoat2_1#1$2","focus":"m","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿黛尔","text":"凯勒老师，我想一个人在这里待一会，可以吗？","id":178,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3e/Avg_avg_1016_agoat2_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_999_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯勒","text":"嗯。","id":180,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/18/Avg_avg_npc_999_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":181},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":182},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":183},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":184},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_paper2","volume":"0.8","id":185},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":186},{"type":"text","text":"女孩将文件一一翻阅过，在那堆陈旧文件的最下面，放着一张手写的信。","id":187},{"type":"dialog","id":188},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":189},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":190},{"type":"sticker","id":191,"multi":"true","text":"<i>“......以上研究资料，来自两位对科学无比忠诚的学者。</i>","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":192},{"type":"sticker","id":193,"multi":"true","text":"<i>“他们将毕生精力，以及生命都奉献于科考工作，寄希望于用知识来保护人类，寻求更安全、美好的家园。</i>","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":194},{"type":"sticker","id":195,"multi":"true","text":"<i>“望予以认真对待，将之用于正确的事业。”</i>","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":196},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":197},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":198},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1016_agoat2_1#4$2","focus":"m","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿黛尔","text":"凯勒老师的名字......原来是......","id":200,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/94/Avg_avg_1016_agoat2_1-4$2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":201},{"type":"charslot","id":202},{"type":"text","text":"信的一角，娟秀的字体写着签名。","id":203},{"type":"dialog","id":204},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":205},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":206},{"type":"sticker","id":207,"multi":"true","text":"<i>“阿黛尔·凯勒”</i>","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.06","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":208},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":209},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":210},{"type":"dialog","id":211},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":212},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":213},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":214},{"type":"charslot","id":215},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9a/Avg_bg_bg_hotel.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":216},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":217},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_shovel","volume":"0.2","loop":"true","channel":"chan","id":218},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/a001/m_dia_path_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":219,"musicid":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":220},{"type":"playsound","key":"$gavel1","volume":"0.5","id":221},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"chan","fadetime":"1","id":222},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":223},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"0.7","id":224},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":225},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4106_bryota_1#8$1","posfrom":"0,-50","posto":"0,0","duration":"0.8","isblock":"false","id":226},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":227},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4106_bryota_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"丽芙！","id":229,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1b/Avg_avg_4106_bryota_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"躺下，别乱动。","id":231,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/60/Avg_avg_348_ceylon_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4106_bryota_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":232},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"丽芙呢——","id":233,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fb/Avg_avg_4106_bryota_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":234},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"冷静点，她已经回家了，小家伙当时吓得不轻，但好在没怎么受伤——现在你才是需要担心的那个。","id":235,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/60/Avg_avg_348_ceylon_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4106_bryota_1#17$1","focus":"m","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"那就好......那就好......","id":237,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fa/Avg_avg_4106_bryota_1-17$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":238},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovementsp","volume":"1","id":239},{"type":"charslot","duration":"0.5","id":240},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":241},{"type":"text","text":"悬着的心放下，少年又嗵的一声倒在病床上。","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"我......晕了几天？","id":243},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"整整三天。","id":245,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/60/Avg_avg_348_ceylon_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"你的妈妈还有弟弟妹妹每天都来看你，你知不知道他们有多担心？","id":246,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/60/Avg_avg_348_ceylon_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1","focus":"none","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"这次就别批评我了，锡兰医生。","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"我也是......为了救人嘛......我还准备好好批评一下那个不听话的妹妹来着......","id":249},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"哼，还想隐瞒。你真当医生什么都看不出来？","id":251,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0d/Avg_avg_348_ceylon_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"你还真是大胆，竟然还偷学源石技艺。你知不知道你被送到这里的时候血液源石结晶密度达到了多高？","id":252,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0d/Avg_avg_348_ceylon_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#10$1","focus":"none","id":253},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"这......","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"这个治疗......很花钱吗？","id":255},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"哼，就算你去罗德岛打工的话，估计也得顶你好一阵工资了。","id":257,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0d/Avg_avg_348_ceylon_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#10$1","focus":"none","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"哈哈......看来这下是真没得选了啊......","id":259},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"但是说起来，我正准备在新汐斯塔建立一个感染者的收治中心。刚刚起步，会需要不少帮手。","id":261,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/60/Avg_avg_348_ceylon_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"要不要考虑一下，留下来帮我的忙？","id":263,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3e/Avg_avg_348_ceylon_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":264},{"type":"charslot","id":265},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"多谢你锡兰医生，但是我已经和家人说好了......短时间内，我还是不留在汐斯塔了。","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"如果可以的话，我更想去你说的那艘可以开往很多地方的船上看看。","id":267},{"type":"dialog","id":268},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":269},{"type":"text","text":"就算不陪在身边，家人也永远是家人。我可以试着为自己而活，做自己真正想做的事。老爹见过的风景，我也想去看看。","id":270},{"type":"text","text":"探险家，听起来的确是很酷的职业。","id":271},{"type":"dialog","id":272},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.3","fadetime":"1.5","id":273},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_shovel","volume":"0.2","loop":"true","channel":"chan1","id":274},{"type":"playsound","key":"$gavel1","volume":"0.5","id":275},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"chan1","fadetime":"2","id":276},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"这是什么声音？","id":278},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"哦，应该是诗怀雅小姐的施工队吧。动作还真快，刚签完合同就要动工了啊。","id":280,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_348_ceylon_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":281},{"type":"charslot","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"纯白火山......","id":283},{"type":"dialog","id":284},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"0.7","id":285},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":286},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4106_bryota_1#8$1","posfrom":"0,-50","posto":"0,0","afrom":"0","ato":"1","duration":"0.5","id":287},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":288},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"锡兰医生！我要先回去一趟，之后会补上医疗费的！","id":289,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1b/Avg_avg_4106_bryota_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":290},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":291},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":292},{"type":"delay","time":"4","id":293},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"1","id":294},{"type":"dialog","id":295},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":296},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_340_shwaz_1#12$1","duration":"1","id":297},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":298},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_340_shwaz_1#12$1","focus":"m","id":299},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑","text":"工作结束了？","id":300,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6b/Avg_avg_340_shwaz_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":301},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"嗯，这是最后一个病人。呼......这几天一直在忙收治中心的事，都没顾得上听你讲你这些日子都做了什么......","id":302,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/60/Avg_avg_348_ceylon_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_340_shwaz_1#12$1","focus":"m","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑","text":"其实也只是一些罗德岛的任务，去了更多国家，也新认识了不少干员。","id":304,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6b/Avg_avg_340_shwaz_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑","text":"等休假结束，我可能会出几次长任务，也有可能在那些地方驻扎一段时间。","id":305,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6b/Avg_avg_340_shwaz_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"唔，虽然很想跟着你一起去，但我现在确实也走不开了。而且，那样肯定也不是你希望的吧？","id":307,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_348_ceylon_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_340_shwaz_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":308},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑","text":"对，那样就没有意义了。","id":309,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d7/Avg_avg_340_shwaz_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":310},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"那这几天我带着你转一转这里吧？","id":311,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_348_ceylon_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_340_shwaz_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑","text":"好啊。这里也比上次回来时看上去更漂亮了。","id":313,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d7/Avg_avg_340_shwaz_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"我有信心等你下次回来，一定是一个更新的汐斯塔。","id":315,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_348_ceylon_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_340_shwaz_1#14$1","focus":"m","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑","text":"我相信，小姐。","id":317,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_340_shwaz_1-14$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":318},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":319},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":320},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0","fadetime":"1.5","id":321},{"type":"charslot","id":322},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/65/Avg_bg_41_g1_siestacommercialstreet_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":323},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":324},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":325},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":326},{"type":"text","text":"还没有完全入秋，阳光依旧热烈，天气仿佛突然凉了不少。在街上玩耍的人似乎多了一点，几家商店门口竟然也排起了队。","id":327},{"type":"dialog","id":328},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":329},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4106_bryota_1#10$1","duration":"1","id":330},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":331},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4106_bryota_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"（拜托了，先别拆，千万先别拆！）","id":333,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fb/Avg_avg_4106_bryota_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"（至少让我再看最后一眼......）","id":334,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fb/Avg_avg_4106_bryota_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_994_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"哈莉","text":"埃尼斯？你不是应该还在病床上躺着——","id":336,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/81/Avg_avg_npc_994_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4106_bryota_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":337},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":338},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"纯白火山拆了吗——","id":339,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1b/Avg_avg_4106_bryota_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":340},{"type":"charslot","id":341},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"2","id":342},{"type":"text","text":"话音未落，埃尼斯看到了店门口全新的灯牌。","id":343},{"type":"text","text":"除了换掉了损坏的灯泡，哈莉还在上面添上了自己的一点涂鸦——一大两小，三只棉花糖一样的小羊。","id":344},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_994_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":345},{"type":"dialogue","name":"哈莉","text":"谁跟你说改建就是拆迁？这里准备要建一个新的水上乐园。","id":346,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_994_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4106_bryota_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":347},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"水上乐园？！那，物流中心呢？","id":348,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1b/Avg_avg_4106_bryota_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_994_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"哈莉","text":"听说市政厅重新规划了方案，新汐斯塔还是要保留一点旅游风景，这条街可以考虑作为景点保留下来。","id":350,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_994_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"哈莉","text":"佩利佩把他的好几家店铺打包卖给了一个外国集团，说是投资人觉得之前举办的活动反响不错，在这里建一个水上乐园也有生意可做。","id":351,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_994_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_994_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":352},{"type":"dialogue","name":"哈莉","text":"这家小店，说不定还能再开一阵子吧。","id":353,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/30/Avg_avg_npc_994_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4106_bryota_1#17$1","focus":"m","id":354},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"闹了这么久，居然......","id":355,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fa/Avg_avg_4106_bryota_1-17$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"妈，这辆车是......？","id":356,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fa/Avg_avg_4106_bryota_1-17$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_994_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":357},{"type":"dialogue","name":"哈莉","text":"喔，是前几天在店里坐过的那位，好像很有钱的大小姐开过来停在这的。","id":358,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/30/Avg_avg_npc_994_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":359},{"type":"charslot","id":360},{"type":"text","text":"一辆崭新纯白色皮卡停在小店门口，雨刷器下压着一张小纸条。","id":361},{"type":"dialog","id":362},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":363},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":364},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“帮朋友解决一些小麻烦。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":365},{"type":"subtitle","id":366},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":367},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":368},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4106_bryota_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":369},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"那个大小姐，就是喜欢耍帅......","id":370,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c2/Avg_avg_4106_bryota_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4106_bryota_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":371},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"......谢啦。","id":372,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/07/Avg_avg_4106_bryota_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":373},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":374},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":375},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":376},{"type":"charslot","id":377},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bb/Avg_bg_bg_ltroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":378},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":379},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$m_dia_street_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_street_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":380,"musicid":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":381},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":382},{"type":"playsound","key":"$transmission","volume":"0.4","id":383},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":384},{"type":"text","text":"“尊敬的亚当斯·施怀雅先生，您好。和往常一样，先祝您身体健康。”","id":385},{"type":"text","text":"“......那么这一次，是我赢了您。”","id":386},{"type":"text","text":"......","id":387},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚当斯","text":"（虚弱的喘息）","id":388},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_2005_weiyw_1#1","focus":"m","id":389},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"要帮你关了电视，还是要帮你叫一下医生？","id":390,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1f/Avg_char_2005_weiyw_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_2005_weiyw_1#1","focus":"none","id":391},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚当斯","text":"不肖子孙。","id":392},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚当斯","text":"总算做了一件......","id":393},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚当斯","text":"呼......","id":394},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_2005_weiyw_1#1","focus":"m","id":395},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"多少年没在你脸上看到这样的表情了，真该叫林一起来的。","id":396,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1f/Avg_char_2005_weiyw_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_2005_weiyw_1#1","focus":"none","id":397},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚当斯","text":"别得意......你早晚也......","id":398},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚当斯","text":"小心年轻人......魏彦吾。","id":399},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚当斯","text":"时间......在他们那边。","id":400},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_2005_weiyw_1#1","focus":"m","id":401},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"他们总会站到我们面前的。","id":402,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1f/Avg_char_2005_weiyw_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_2005_weiyw_1#1","focus":"none","id":403},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚当斯","text":"我已经等不及......要看......将来晖洁......给你寄来信的时候......","id":404},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_2005_weiyw_1#1","focus":"m","id":405},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"那我也是。","id":406,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1f/Avg_char_2005_weiyw_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_2005_weiyw_1#1","focus":"none","id":407},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚当斯","text":"哈......哈哈......","id":408},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚当斯","text":"哈哈哈哈......","id":409},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_2005_weiyw_1#1","focus":"m","id":410},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"哈哈哈哈哈！","id":411,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1f/Avg_char_2005_weiyw_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_2005_weiyw_1#1","focus":"none","id":412},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":413},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚当斯","text":"哈哈哈呃——","id":414},{"type":"dialog","id":415},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":416},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_medicalbeep","channel":"a","loop":"true","id":417},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":418},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_2005_weiyw_1#2","focus":"m","id":419},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"喂，老病虎？","id":420,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e1/Avg_char_2005_weiyw_2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_2005_weiyw_1#3","focus":"m","id":421},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":422},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"喂，喂！","id":423,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/92/Avg_char_2005_weiyw_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"大夫，大夫！","id":424,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/92/Avg_char_2005_weiyw_3.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":425},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"a","fadetime":"2","id":426},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":427},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":428},{"type":"charslot","id":429},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/69/Avg_41_i13_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":430},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":431},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_warm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":432,"musicid":4},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_penrustle","volume":"1","id":433},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":434},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_penrustle","volume":"1","id":435},{"type":"text","text":"<i>亲爱的爸爸妈妈：</i>","id":436},{"type":"text","text":"<i>展信佳。</i>","id":437},{"type":"text","text":"<i>我最近很好，我来到了汐斯塔，度过了一个难忘的夏天。</i>","id":438},{"type":"text","text":"<i>这里与你们曾经见过的样子已大不相同，但依然是一座很有趣的城市。</i>","id":439},{"type":"text","text":"<i>我也登上了汐斯塔火山，顺利完成了这一次的观测，得到了很有价值的科研数据。</i>","id":440},{"type":"dialog","id":441},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_penrustle","volume":"1","id":442},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"-350","yFrom":"0","xTo":"-250","yTo":"-0","xScaleFrom":"1.6","yScaleFrom":"1.6","xScaleTo":"1.6","yScaleTo":"1.6","duration":"20","block":"false","id":443},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":444},{"type":"text","text":"<i>我在这里见到了一位你们以前的朋友，不，应该说是两位。</i>","id":445},{"type":"text","text":"<i>他们给我讲了许多，咖啡厅的相遇、硫酸池里的落水、实验室中的故事，各种各样我不曾知道的，你们年轻时候的事情。</i>","id":446},{"type":"text","text":"<i>有“人”告诉我，“一切过去的事都不会真的过去，它们总会换一种方式陪在你的身边”。</i>","id":447},{"type":"text","text":"<i>我现在更有理由相信这句话，因为我有了一段神奇的经历。</i>","id":448},{"type":"text","text":"<i>像是小时候你们给我讲的睡前故事那样，或许有那么一部分是虚构的，但我很愿意，也很希望自己去相信。</i>","id":449},{"type":"dialog","id":450},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_penrustle","volume":"1","id":451},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/69/Avg_41_i13_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"3","xScale":"1.6","yScale":"1.6","x":"300","id":452},{"type":"imagetween","image":"41_i13_1","fadetime":"0.5","xScaleFrom":"1.6","yScaleFrom":"1.6","xScaleTo":"1.6","yScaleTo":"1.6","xTo":"200","duration":"20","id":453},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":454},{"type":"text","text":"<i>爸爸妈妈，我应该承认，我从来不如自己想象的坚强。</i>","id":455},{"type":"text","text":"<i>我害怕自己会听不见任何声音，害怕眼前的事物会变得一团模糊，害怕最后带走我生命的不是火山、研究，而是矿石病的病痛和折磨。</i>","id":456},{"type":"text","text":"<i>如果可以的话，我希望自己能走过所有你们曾走过的火山，研究完你们留下的笔记上的每一个疑问。</i>","id":457},{"type":"text","text":"<i>试着冒险在硫酸湖里划一次船，假装自己也是一颗小小的，在熔岩中燃烧着的石头。</i>","id":458},{"type":"dialog","id":459},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_penrustle","volume":"1","id":460},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/69/Avg_41_i13_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":461},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":462},{"type":"text","text":"<i>恐惧不是勇气的反义词，正如死亡也不是生命的对立面，我热爱火山研究，我也同样热爱我的生命。</i>","id":463},{"type":"text","text":"<i>或许，我应该有更快乐一点的方法。不过我现在才明白这些，算晚吗？</i>","id":464},{"type":"text","text":"<i>其实我并不知道该将这封信寄到哪里，我只是很想让你们知道......</i>","id":465},{"type":"dialog","id":466},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_penrustle","volume":"1","id":467},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":468},{"type":"text","text":"<i>我在这里很好。</i>","id":469},{"type":"text","text":"<i>......</i>","id":470},{"type":"dialog","id":471},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":472},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorknockquite","id":473},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ac/Avg_41_i13_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":474},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","delay":"1","id":475},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":476},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"阿黛尔小姐，您是要寄信吗？直接给我吧，我送信的时候可以顺手带过去。","id":477},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"这是要寄到哪去的信？","id":478},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿黛尔","text":"嗯......","id":479},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿黛尔","text":"还是不用啦，我想自己把这封信送出去。","id":480},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿黛尔","text":"埃尼斯先生，这朵花是——","id":481},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"啊，这还是我之前偷偷挖黑曜石的时候在山坡上挖的，本来是想送给丽芙他们当礼物的。可是从火山上带下来后，它的颜色好像就变了。","id":482},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿黛尔","text":"是汐斯塔火山吗！","id":483},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃尼斯","text":"是啊，就在火山的背面。","id":484},{"type":"dialog","id":485},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":486},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":487},{"type":"image","id":488},{"type":"charslot","id":489},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":490},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":491},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":492},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":493},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_penrustle","volume":"1","id":494},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":495},{"type":"text","text":"<i>......</i>","id":496},{"type":"text","text":"<i>对了，你们本来要在汐斯塔找的东西，我也找到啦。</i>","id":497},{"type":"dialog","id":498},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0","fadetime":"1","id":499},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":500},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":501},{"type":"charslot","id":502},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/57/Avg_bg_41_g11_volcanomountainside.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":503},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":504},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"1","id":505},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":506},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":507},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1006_1#1$1","duration":"0.7","id":508},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1007_1#1$1","duration":"0.7","id":509},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":510},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1007_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":511},{"type":"dialogue","name":"温和的生物","text":"（很美丽的火山。）","id":512,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b3/Avg_avg_npc_1007_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"温和的生物","text":"（火山在爆发的时候才是最美丽的，虽然只有短短一瞬。）","id":513,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b3/Avg_avg_npc_1007_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"温和的生物","text":"（想看到它下一次爆发，还要等多久呢？）","id":514,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b3/Avg_avg_npc_1007_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1006_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":515},{"type":"dialogue","name":"严肃的生物","text":"（没关系，我们可以留在这里多等一会。）","id":516,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c6/Avg_avg_npc_1006_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"严肃的生物","text":"（我们还有很多时间。）","id":517,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c6/Avg_avg_npc_1006_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":518},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":519},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":520},{"type":"charslot","id":521},{"type":"image","id":522}],"characters":["寻找汐斯塔的少女","大帝","伯德","阿黛尔","凯勒","埃尼斯","锡兰","黑","哈莉","亚当斯","魏彦吾","温和的生物","严肃的生物"]}